OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBan cyclists and e-scooter 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Friders using phones, Tory  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpeer urges                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Tory politician is calling for a ban 
OL,6, on using mobiles while on a bicycle or 
OL,7, e-scooter, after a concerning incident 
OL,8, with a cyclist near Parliament.        
OL,10,FBaroness McIntosh of Pickering wants a 
OL,11,Flaw change so cyclists are prosecuted  
OL,12,Ffor the offence of using a phone, in   
OL,13,Fthe same way that car drivers are.     
OL,15,FThere is no specific offence for a     
OL,16,Fcyclist using a phone, but a minister  
OL,17,Fpointed out cyclists can be prosecuted 
OL,18,Ffor careless or dangerous cycling.     
OL,20,FThat comes with fines of up to #2,500. 
